{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/make-images-mobile-responsive","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Napravite da slike budu prilagodljive za mobilne telefone","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Prvo, dodajte novu sliku ispod postojeće. Postavite atribut <code>src</code> elementa na <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg</code>.</p>\n<p>Biće dobro ako će ova slika imati istu širinu kao ekran našeg mobilnog telefona.</p>\n<p>Srećom, koristeći Bootstrap, samo moramo dodati klasu <code>img-responsive</code> na vašu sliku. Uradite to, i slika bi trebalo da savršeno odgovara širini vaše stranice.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9acde08812","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18232,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/make-images-mobile-responsive"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  .red-text {\r\n    color: red;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  p {\r\n    font-size: 16px;\r\n    font-family: Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .smaller-image {\r\n    width: 100px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"red-text\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n\r\n  <p>Click here for <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n  <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"smaller-image thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n\r\n  <p>Things cats love:</p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate ukupno dve slike.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('img'), 2);"},{"text":"<p>Vaša nova slika treba da bude ispod stare i da ima klasu <code>img-responsive</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[1]?.classList?.contains('img-responsive'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaša nova slika ne sme imati klasu <code>smaller-image</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFalse(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[1]?.classList?.contains('smaller-image'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaša nova slika mora imati atribut <code>src</code> sa vrednošću <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[1]?.getAttri